Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! Really spacious and durable travel bag designed for comfortable carrying and easy handling on long journeys all over the world. Made from G-1000 Heavy-duty, an extra hardwearing version of Fjallraven's durable outdoor fabric, with a base in waterproof PU-laminated nylon. The bag can be carried both by hand and as a backpack. Handles with grips in natural-toned leather. The shoulder straps are padded and even the top of the bag has padded panels to keep contents from pressing against the back. The smart design of the side pockets and top section allows handles and shoulder straps to be stowed away, making airport check-ins easier and reducing the risk of the bag getting caught on something during transport. Double handles on the ends make it easy to get hold of and give a stable grip when loading/unloading. The main compartment has an extra large zippered opening and a mesh pocket inside to keep small items in place. On the outside there are two open side pockets, one with a zippered pocket for items needed close at hand. Volume: 110 liters. - Pockets: 1 interior zip, 2 exterior Fjallraven Duffel No. 6 Bag, Black, Large
